    "custom_grub_terra_features_WJqKT3": {
      "type": "custom-grub-terra-features",
      "blocks": {
        "text_V44abN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>RAISED IN USA & CANADA</strong></h3><p>All our larvae are grown in Canada, the United States, Costa Rica, and Indonesia. Never from China!</p><h3><strong>STRONGER EGGSHELLS</strong></h3><p>With 75x more calcium than mealworms, GrubTerra grubs will help your flock lay more eggs. With stronger shell.</p><h3><strong>Increased Egg Production</strong></h3><p>GrubTerras Grubs promote stronger eggshells and help hens increase their energy levels and egg production. Grubterra Grubs are also a great supplement during molting season and in the cold winter months!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_V44abN"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "GrubTerra Black Soldier Fly Larvae Proven to Increase Egg production",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_39.png",
        "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_244_7.png",
        "image_position": "left",
        "padding_top": 40,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "custom_grub_terra_features_Gd8Wnq": {
      "type": "custom-grub-terra-features",
      "blocks": {
        "text_zUxAJX": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>NO PRESERVATIVES</strong></h3><p>No additives. No preservatives. Our larvae are also great for ducks, turkeys, and other fowl, as well as wild birds and fish!</p><h3><strong>NUTRITIOUS DIETS</strong></h3><p>GrubTerra’s black soldier fly larvae are raised on a nutritious diet of vegetables, fruits, and carbohydrates giving them a healthy balanced diet.</p><h3><strong>SUSTAINABLY RAISED</strong></h3><p>GrubTerra’s black soldier fly larvae are raised off of food waste that would have been thrown into landfills and for every 1 pound of grubs purchased 20 pounds of waste was diverted from landfills</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_zUxAJX"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_39_1.png",
        "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/Dried_Black_Soldier_Fly_Larvae.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "testimonial_XFGeCf": {
      "type": "testimonial",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_GwCXVi": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_775.png",
            "stars": "shopify://shop_images/image_41.svg",
            "author": "Jay. C and Lisa. C",
            "text": "<p>The amount of eggs we get now is CRAZY!!! We have 6 chickens. Before we started feeding them GrubTerra we were lucky to get 1-2 eggs a day. Now we are getting 4-5 a day! We feed Black soldier fly larvae to our chickens every day and the health of our birds has never been better. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
